						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">rychan wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Ah, so I don't need to set it out as 2 16kb banks then? just one solid 32kb bank.</div><br />Right. The reason NES Space Checker displays everything as 16 KB banks is that the iNES ROM file format header stores the ROM size as a multiple of 16 KB.</div>

					
